      info        : "Browser pop-up windows have long been one of the most annoying delivery mechanisms of unwanted web content. The content can be unwanted content, including Not Safe For Work, or malicious content relying on a user interacting with the pop-up. Safari has a built-in capability to disable pop-ups that should be enabled.

